<div id="review_3391908331" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3391908331" />
    <a title="Abbie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/101124941-abbie"><img alt="Abbie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1584222359p2/101124941.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3391908331?book_show_action=true">Jun 18, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Abbie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Abbie" href="/user/show/101124941-abbie">Abbie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780830772605" href="/book/show/35721783-tortured-for-christ">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3391908331" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8121529051289044715">So cool to see a man’s heart for his enemies after going through 14 years of prison and torture. Not only must we love our enemies, we must love our fellow brethren in chains. Wurmbrand calls us to remember and labor with our brothers and sisters who are even now being persecuted for the name of Christ.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


